      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>When you see something demonstrated you can replicate it, even if you are not skilled in the task.</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When an ally you can carefully observe attempts a skill check for a skill that is not a class skill for you and that you are not trained in, you can watch them and attempt to replicate what they do. You gain a +3 insight bonus to a skill check for the same action you observed so long as you make your attempt within 1 minute. You cannot use this ability to attempt an action that requires being trained.</p>"
